OL,3,GStrathclyde
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FIt is
OL,6,Fexpected to be a cloudy but dry
OL,7,Fevening across most parts. Cloud will
OL,8,Fthicken overnight with some rain
OL,9,Fspreading into Argyll by the morning.
OL,10,
OL,11,CSunday:FCloudy with outbreaks of rain
OL,12,Facross Argyll. Mainly dry with bright
OL,13,Fspells elsewhere and feeling warm.
OL,14,
OL,15,COutlook for Monday to Wednesday:FCloud
OL,16,Fand rain across Argyll will clear
OL,17,Fduring Monday. Otherwise it will be
OL,18,Fdry with plenty of warm sunshine
OL,19,Fexpected.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
